---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Alembic Pharma Paperless Validation Success - GoVal">
  <Navigation />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-blue">
    <div class="container hero-container">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <p class="section-label">Alembic's Digital Leap:</p>
        <h1>100% Paperless Validation Success with GoVal</h1>
        <p class="hero-description">
          With a legacy of over 100 years, Alembic Pharmaceuticals, a leader in therapeutic segments like cardiovascular and CNS, embarked on a digital transformation journey to modernize its validation processes and uphold its commitment to quality.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
          <a href="/contact-us" class="btn btn-secondary" rel="noopener">
            Talk to Our Consultant
            <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/>
              <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="/images/alembic-m .jpg" alt="Alembic Pharmaceuticals Paperless Validation Success" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Addressing Key Validation Challenges -->
  <section class="content">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="content-label">[ FROM MANUAL TO DIGITAL ]</p>
      <h2>The Challenge of Paper-Based Validation at Scale</h2>
      <p>
        Before partnering with GoVal, Alembic's manual validation processes were resource-intensive. In a single year, the company conducted <strong>343 CSVs</strong>, a monumental effort that consumed <strong>9,336.5 days</strong> and generated <strong>380,000 pages</strong> of paper. With an average completion time of <strong>25 days per CSV</strong>, the process was slow and susceptible to data integrity issues and GDP errors.
      </p>
      <div class="solution-logo-container">
        <img src="/images/alembic-logo.png" alt="Alembic Pharmaceuticals Logo" class="solution-logo" />
      </div>
      <p>They needed a solution to:</p>
      
      <!-- Logo Inserted Here -->
      

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Eliminate manual errors</strong> and resolve GDP/DI issues.</li>
        <li><strong>Drastically reduce validation timelines</strong> and operational costs.</li>
        <li><strong>Automate the creation</strong> of critical reports like the RTM and VSR.</li>
        <li><strong>Harmonize validation practices</strong> across all their locations.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Rapid Transformation Section -->
  <section class="rapid-transformation">
    <div class="container rapid-flex">
      <div class="rapid-text">
        <p class="content-label">[ RAPID TRANSFORMATION ]</p>
        <h2 class="rapid-title">GoVal's Accelerated Digital Validation Solution</h2>
        <p class="rapid-desc">
          GoVal provided a comprehensive Validation Lifecycle Management System (VLMS) that transformed Alembic's validation processes, delivering a 100% digital, paperless environment with remarkable speed and efficiency.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="rapid-cards-row">
        <div class="rapid-card">
          <span class="rapid-icon">
            <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FF9800"><path d="M12 2l9 4v6c0 5-3.9 9.7-9 11-5.1-1.3-9-6-9-11V6l9-4zm0 8.3V4.2l-7 3.1V12c0 4.1 3.1 8.1 7 9.4 3.9-1.3 7-5.3 7-9.4V7.3l-7-3.1v6.1z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Zero Paper, Printing & Scanning</h3>
          <p>GoVal completely eliminated the need for physical documents, saving 3.8 lac pages annually and removing storage and retrieval costs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rapid-card">
          <span class="rapid-icon">
            <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FF9800"><path d="M19.14 12.936c.035-.298.059-.6.059-.936s-.024-.638-.07-.936l2.036-1.589a.5.5 0 00.121-.61l-1.927-3.332a.5.5 0 00-.602-.229l-2.398.96a7.035 7.035 0 00-1.617-.938l-.364-2.541A.488.488 0 0014.002 2h-4.002a.488.488 0 00-.488.419l-.364 2.541a7.078 7.078 0 00-1.616.938l-2.398-.96a.5.5 0 00-.602.229l-1.926 3.332a.5.5 0 00.12.61l2.036 1.589a7.12 7.12 0 00-.07.936c0 .316.024.638.07.936l-2.036 1.589a.5.5 0 00-.12.61l1.926 3.332a.5.5 0 00.602.228l2.398-.96c.5.382 1.046.705 1.616.938l.364 2.541a.488.488 0 00.488.419h4.002a.488.488 0 00.488-.419l.364-2.541a7.08 7.08 0 001.617-.938l2.398.96a.495.495 0 00.602-.228l1.927-3.332a.5.5 0 00-.12-.61l-2.036-1.589zm-7.14 2.564a3.5 3.5 0 110-7 3.5 3.5 0 010 7z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Massive Time Savings</h3>
          <p>With an average saving of 5 days per CSV, Alembic reclaimed 1,955 validation days per year through automated workflows and faster test execution.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rapid-card">
          <span class="rapid-icon">
            <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#FF9800"><path d="M7 2v13h3v7l7-12h-4l4-8z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Instant Audit Readiness</h3>
          <p>A centralized digital repository and automated traceability matrix ensure all documents are audit-ready 24/7 across all geographical locations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Validation Reimagined Section -->
  <section class="content benefits-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="content-label">[ VALIDATION REIMAGINED ]</p>
      <h2>GoVal's Proven Business Advantages</h2>
      <ul class="benefits-list">
        <li><strong>Improved Compliance</strong>: ALCOA+ principles are maintained through automated workflows and an electronic review and approval process, eliminating GDP and DI issues.</li>
        <li><strong>Automated Workflows</strong>: Deliverables-based review and approval workflows with automatic alerts and notifications eliminate physical document movement.</li>
        <li><strong>Cost Savings</strong>: Reduced storage, retrieval, and archival costs, combined with resource and lifecycle optimization, delivered significant financial benefits.</li>
        <li><strong>Harmonized Practices</strong>: GoVal enabled consistent validation practices across all of Alembic's locations, with the ability to extend documents to other sites.</li>
        <li><strong>Automated Reporting</strong>: The Traceability Matrix (RTM) and Validation Summary Report (VSR) are automatically prepared, saving 3-4 days per CSV.</li>
        <li><strong>Real-Time Visibility</strong>: A real-time status dashboard provides complete visibility of progress, enhancing project management and continued compliance.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* Exact styling from the example file */
html { font-size: 100%; }
body { font-size: 1rem; }
.hero-blue { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16407d 0%, #092143 100%); color: #fff; padding: 3rem 1rem 2rem; }
.hero-container { max-width: 1200px; margin: auto; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
.hero-text { max-width: 480px; flex: 1 1 600px; padding-right: 2rem; }
.section-label { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.13em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #ff7800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.hero-text h1 { font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
.hero-description { font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; color: #e1e7f6; }
.hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1.1rem; }
.btn { font-weight: 700; padding: 0.63em 1.25em; border-radius: 0.55em; cursor: pointer; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.32em; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: background 0.25s; border: none; }
.btn-secondary { color: #ff7800; border: 2px solid #ff7800; background: transparent; }
.btn-secondary:hover, .btn-secondary:focus { background-color: #ff7800; color: #fff; }
.icon { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
.hero-image { max-width: 600px; flex: 1 1 400px; text-align: right; }
.hero-image img { width: 100%; border-radius: 13px; box-shadow: 0 11px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
.rapid-transformation { background: #fff; padding: 3.5rem 0 2.4rem; }
.rapid-flex { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 2.5rem; max-width: 1200px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 2.8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.rapid-text { flex: 1 1 400px; margin-top: 1.2rem; }
.content-label { color: #111827; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.7rem; }
.rapid-title { font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: #14213d; }
.rapid-desc { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151; }
.rapid-cards-row { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; gap: 2.2rem; justify-content: space-between; align-items: stretch; }
.rapid-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); padding: 1.9rem 1.1rem 1.4rem; min-width: 260px; max-width: 340px; flex: 1 1 0px; text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start; }
.rapid-card h3 { margin: 0.7em 0 0.4em; font-size: 1.13rem; font-weight: bold; color: #112557; }
.rapid-card p { font-size: 0.99em; color: #42526e; }
.rapid-badge { font-size: 0.90rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; border-radius: 13px; background: #1878ca; padding: 0.32em 1.15em; margin-bottom: 0.3em; display: inline-block; }
.benefits-section { max-width: 720px; margin: 3rem auto 6rem; }
.benefits-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
.benefits-list li { padding-left: 2rem; position: relative; padding-bottom: 0.8rem; font-size: 1rem; }
.benefits-list li strong { font-weight: 800; color: #17233d; }
.benefits-list li::before { content: '✔'; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.25rem; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #2072c5; }
.content { max-width: 720px; margin: 1rem auto 3rem; padding: 0 1rem; color: #17233d; text-align: center; }
.content ul { text-align: left; max-width: 600px; margin: 0.5rem auto 0 auto; }
.content h2 { font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 0.9rem; }
.content p, .content ul { font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
@media (max-width: 1000px) { .hero-container { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; } .hero-text { padding-right: 0; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; } .hero-image img { max-width: 90%; } .rapid-cards-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; } }
@media (max-width: 550px) { .hero-text h1 { font-size: 2rem; } .hero-description, .rapid-desc, .benefits-list li { font-size: 1rem; } .rapid-card h3 { font-size: 1.13rem; } .btn { font-size: 1rem; } }

/* --- STYLES FOR LOGO IN CONTENT --- */
.solution-logo-container {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 2rem 0;
}
.solution-logo {
    max-height: 70px;
    width: auto;
}
</style>

